<div style="text-align: left">Dawn of the Carboniferous. Plants mostly small (the late Devonian forests gone), first terrestrial <a href="../../vertebrates/tetrapoda/index.html">tetrapods</a> appear. Marine and freshwater life furnishes. Sharks diversify to take up ecological niches vacated by the placoderms</div></td>
