<div style="text-align: left">Carboniferous flora flourishes. Giant amphibious eurypterids. <a href="../../vertebrates/tetrapoda/index.html">Tetrapods</a> become common and diverse, including both terrestrial and aquatic forms. The first pre- or proto-amniotes appear on land</div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="mis3">
<big><a href="serpukhovian.html">The Serpukhovian</a></big> <br />
<div style="text-align: left">Euramerica tropical and dominated by huge forests - the "coal swamp" biome. Dramatic evolutionary radiation of insects; flight appears (flying insects). The giant arthropleurids appear. <a href="../../vertebrates/tetrapoda/index.html">Tetrapods</a> flourish, with primitive forms co-existing alongside more advanced ones.</div></td>
</tr>
